A top-tier B Tech Admission 2023 education is provided by Shivalik College of Engineering, a renowned engineering college in India. The institution is situated in the lovely Uttarakhand city of Dehradun.
With the goal of offering top-notch engineering education to students from around the nation, Shivalik College of Engineering was founded in 2006. The All-India Council for Technical Education has authorised the college, which is connected with the Uttarakhand Technical University (AICTE).
